query utilsQuery {
  user {
    id
    accountAvailable
    accountTotal
  }
  authUser {
    id
    name
    apellidoPaterno
    apellidoMaterno
    RFC
    CURP
    clabe
    mobile
    isLender
    isBorrower
    isSupport
    language
    email
  }
}

query MyInvestmentsQueriesPaginationUser(
  $count: Int = 5
  $cursor: String = ""
  $reset: Float = 0
  $status: [InvestmentStatus!] = null
  $id: ID!
) {
  node(id: $id) {
    __typename
    ...MyInvestmentsQueries_user_2YVuhV
    id
  }
}

fragment MyInvestmentsQueriesRow_investment on Investment {
  id
  borrower_id
  loan_id
  quantity
  created_at
  updated_at
  status
  payments
  ROI
  term
  moratory
  interest_to_earn
  paid_already
  to_be_paid
}

fragment MyInvestmentsQueries_user_2YVuhV on User {
  investments(first: $count, after: $cursor, status: $status, reset: $reset) {
    edges {
      node {
        id
        borrower_id
        loan_id
        quantity
        created_at
        updated_at
        status
        payments
        ROI
        term
        moratory
        interest_to_earn
        paid_already
        to_be_paid
        ...MyInvestmentsQueriesRow_investment
        __typename
      }
      cursor
    }
    pageInfo {
      endCursor
      hasNextPage
    }
  }
  id
}

subscription MyInvestmentsQueriesSubscription(
  $status: [InvestmentStatus!]
) {
  investments_subscribe_insert(status: $status) {
    node {
      id
      borrower_id
      lender_id
      loan_id
      quantity
      ROI
      payments
      term
      moratory
      created_at
      updated_at
      status
      interest_to_earn
      paid_already
      to_be_paid
    }
    cursor
  }
}

subscription MyInvestmentsQueriesUpdateSubscription {
  investments_subscribe_update {
    id
    borrower_id
    lender_id
    loan_id
    quantity
    ROI
    payments
    term
    moratory
    created_at
    updated_at
    status
    interest_to_earn
    paid_already
    to_be_paid
  }
}

query MyInvestmentRowRefetchQuery(
  $id: ID!
) {
  node(id: $id) {
    __typename
    ...MyInvestmentsQueriesRow_investment
    id
  }
}

fragment MyInvestmentsQueriesRow_investment on Investment {
  id
  borrower_id
  loan_id
  quantity
  created_at
  updated_at
  status
  payments
  ROI
  term

  interest_to_earn
